{"tid":121894,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實啲南亞人係講啲咩語言多？","createTime":"2017-02-15T14:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T15:26:28.000Z","uid":14575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d529b866253b2137e3c82ca4107d61504da013f","tid":121894,"uid":14575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:52:22.000Z","msg":"好似淨係印度都幾十種唔同語言，有冇巴打知究竟喺香港嘅南亞人係講咩語言多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02cd4530e9e8b802e36c06dcfbfbc0576b87c7cd","tid":121894,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T15:04:21.000Z","msg":"印度通常用 Hindi/English - 情況類似 &quot;普通話&quot; <br />\n巴基斯坦既 Urdu 同 Hindi 又非常近似, 所以佢地兩族人溝通唔大問題<br />\n尼泊爾講尼泊爾文, 有朋友話佢地都會講梵文, 但比較少, 不過一般都識講/聽 Hindi"},{"pid":"7bf424c6f3e76b67ac0a18eaa8d49d100ba96b4b","tid":121894,"uid":14575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T15:07:45.000Z","msg":"咁係咪理論上學Hindu 同 Urdu就可以同大部分南亞人溝通到？"},{"pid":"9f40744ed4df66e042ed462d7ad38ecbf2aef422","tid":121894,"uid":14575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T15:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁係咪理論上學Hindi 同 Urdu就可以同大部分南亞人溝通到？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"477348ee978628e15f0233c368369a7a281dd407","tid":121894,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T15:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁係咪理論上學Hindu 同 Urdu就可以同大部分南亞人溝通到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，講應該無問題, 但寫法好唔同, <br />\n詳細真係要問連登既南亞巴絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7285b2012d895f471ce6fb5b7c9e1556c7111a1b","tid":121894,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T15:13:04.000Z","msg":"啲尼泊爾人成日講sa de, 意思係朋友咁解"},{"pid":"8539ec8e6633c3bc9997c05a07799b69ef87274b","tid":121894,"uid":27560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T15:14:43.000Z","msg":"英國人講英語，南亞人講南語"},{"pid":"9cc20aa29eb54